↓

Server

↓

Verify Credentials

↓

Create Session

↓

Store Session

↓

Set-Cookie

↓

Browser Stores Cookie

↓

Future Requests

↓

Cookie Header Sent

↓

Server Finds Session

↓

User Authenticated
```

---

# Cookie vs Session

| Cookie | Session |
|---------|----------|
| Stored in Browser | Stored on Server |
| Contains Session ID | Contains User Information |
| Sent with every request | Used by the server to identify the user |
| Can be viewed in browser | Hidden from users |

Remember:

Cookies identify the session.

Sessions identify the user.

